headline: JQ Medical Appoints Ryan Schorr as Chief Executive Officer
summary: JQ Medical, a leading provider of diabetes supplies and patient support services, announced the appointment of Ryan Schorr as Chief Executive Officer and to its Board of Directors, which he assumed on June 16th, 2025. Schorr succeeds Matt Gallagher and will lead the company through its next phase of growth, focused on the patient experience, operational excellence and expansion into new markets.
